### About the word data

english3.txt is the whole download of 194k words from http://www.gwicks.net/dictionaries.htm
parse with make_dict.rb to generate just the 5 letter words for input validation as dict.txt

lemma.csv is common words by frequency from https://www.kilgarriff.co.uk/BNClists/lemma.num
Using lemma for the target words only. 

### How to Play

To play the game on CLI `ruby play.rb`
To play the web version `ruby index.rb` and go to http://localhost:4567/

### Dev Stuff

To run a full build `bundle install && rake`

To run just tests `rake test`

To spin up a localhost version of the app `rake server` or `rake s` for short
